deck: Alex Ogle is a visual storyteller and freelance comic book artist based in Chattanooga, TN. He has had several successful Comic Book Kickstarter projects and illustrates a series called “Midnight Over Stellar City” for Action Lab Entertainment. He also freelance illustrates for Marvel and does t-shirt designs for WeLoveFine.com.
